item.title: Web Development
item.description: Do you like this website? Thanks so much, I built it myself you know. At this time I only know how to do create static sites. And, my availability to do so will likely be pretty limited this year. But if the price and timing is right, I’d love to help you our with your online project!

item.title: Art Prints
item.description: Online Print Store I do not intent to make this a priority. In fact, as much as possible I’d prefer to NOT commodify my art. However, we live in the real world and if a passive income can be made that can help fund other decommodified art, then maybe this is okay. If you like my art and would like a print, whether it’s currently on the store or not, I can make them them available for you.

item.title: Drone Services
item.description: I am a FAA Part 107 Commercial Drone Pilot. Let me fly for you! Services include: photography, cinematography, home inspections, and more is on the way. My Experience I’ve flown for about two years with my current job but do not have a portfolio since it’s their intelectual property.
